    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and the interior remains pristine with that new-car smell and no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Every feature functions perfectly, and the mechanical components have been meticulously maintained to ensure a smooth, powerful driving experience. A buyer can expect a car that requires zero immediate investment and represents the highest possible standard for a pre-owned vehicle.",
