    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable workhorse with a bit of character? This vehicle has seen plenty of life and is ready for a dedicated new owner to give it some TLC! While the body and interior show significant wear and it will definitely need some mechanical attention soon, it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to get into a luxury model at a fraction of the usual cost. Perfect for a mechanic's special or someone looking for a high-value restoration project!",
      "price": 7500.0,
